Just built an intelligent SQL Chatbot with Streamlit + LangChain + Groq!
Now you can query your database in plain English and get real-time responses — all powered by LLaMA 3 and connected to a live SQL database.

✨ Key Features:
✅ Natural language to SQL conversion
✅ Instant database querying
✅ Clean tabular output
✅ Lightweight Streamlit UI

Perfect for internal dashboards, support tools, or data-driven insights without writing SQL!
